author: Jonathan Sawyer
title: Untitled Han Solo ‘Star Wars’ Movie Officially Starts Filming
text:
While the movie still has yet to receive a title, work on the upcoming Han Solo Star Wars film has begun in the form of principal photography at Pinewood Studios in London. Above we get our first look at some of the key members of the cast.
The new Star Wars picture centers around adventures before the events of Star Wars: A New Hope , including early encounters with the other card-playing rogue from a galaxy far, far away, Lando Calrissian.
The cast includes Alden Ehrenreich as Han Solo, Woody Harrelson , Emilia Clarke, Donald Glover as Lando Calrissian , Thandie Newton, Phoebe Waller-Bridge, Joonas Suotamo as Chewbacca, as direction comes from Phil Lord and Christopher Miller.
“Watching such inspired people from all over the world, with such unique voices, come together for the sole purpose of making art, is nothing short of miraculous,” Lord and Miller said. “We can’t think of anything funny to say, because we just feel really moved, and really lucky.”
The yet-to-be-titled Han Solo Star Wars film is scheduled to arrive on May 25 of next year.
